Wanted to share my directors showreel from 2022! 🎥 
So thankful I get the opportunity continually work with such amazing brands, people, and teams who trust me to bring their creative ideas to life 🖤
Hard to believe we are already 1/3 of the way through 2023, but it’s shaping up to already be a great year of amazing projects #filmmaker #director #directorofphotography
Paris photo dump part 1 🇫🇷🖤
Wrapped an amazing production in Greece last week! First time in the country and the views did not disappoint 🖤

With taking delivery of our full inventory of sunglasses I am one step closer to launching my brand @evokeamore The journey so far has been the most challenging undertaking  of my life but have learned and grown with every bump & stumble along the way. Thank you to everyone for the support thus far and I can’t wait to really get going as this is just the beginning 🖤 would love to know which style do you guys like best?
Some captured moments from Bali 🌴 #cinematic #cinematography

Official launch date for @evokeamore is September 18th, 2023 🚀 Sign up in bio for early access 🖤 Pretty surreal making this vision come to life. Thank you to everyone who’s helped along the journey and supported thus far 🫶

My fashion brand Evoke Amore is LIVE! Link in my bio to shop 🖤 This has been one hell of a journey and has challenged me both entrepreneurially and creatively like never before in my life. I’m so proud with what I’ve built with the brand and know this is just the beginning 🚀

When I started on the journey of creating @evokeamore I knew basically nothing about about creating a tangible luxury product. I was extremely hesitant to even start the process but knew there was no better way than to dive in head first. There were definitely bumps along the way but in building the brand I’ve had to wear many different hats and learned to many new skills that are now so valuable. Thank you all for making the launch yesterday a success 🖤 #clothingbrand #streetwear #luxuryfashion

Our new jacket designs are Archie approved 🐾 what do you guys think? 

#fashion #mensfashion #streetwear #clothingbrand #fashioninspo #mensstyle #menswear #luxuryfashion

Our Black Friday sale for my brand @evokeamore is now live! Get 30% off site wide until Nov 29th. Go treat yourself or grab a gift for someone 🖤 (shop the link in my bio, the discount is automatically applied at checkout)

Some guys (including me) can be tough to shop for 😅 Hopefully this series of gift guides I’ll be making will make things easier for you all this year 🤌 #mensfashion #mensgiftideas #giftideas #holidaygiftguide
